preAuthSteps.header:
Setup BigCommerce Integration
Refer to our documentation for setup instructions
Fill in the below details to establish connection between BigCommerce and Warehouse for data replication

attributes.label: Integration Name
attributes.name: integrationName
attributes.help: Enter the integration name. Daton will use this name to create tables in the warehouse. Once selected, this name cannot be changed.

attributes.label: Frequency
attributes.name: frequency
attributes.help: Select the frequency in hours with which you'd like Daton to pull data from this source.

attributes.label: History
attributes.name: history
attributes.help: Select the number of years of historical data you'd like Daton to pull into your data warehouse.

preAuthSteps.header:
Enter Store Details
Refer to our documentation for setup instructions

attributes.label: Store Hash
attributes.name: storeHash
attributes.description: e.g storehash, if your BigCommerce API path is ex: https://api.bigcommerce.com/stores/storehash/v3/

attributes.label: Client ID
attributes.name: clientId
attributes.description: Please enter the Client ID associated with the store key that was generated.

attributes.label: Access Token
attributes.name: accessToken
attributes.description: Please enter the access token associated with the store key that was generated.
